<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink334">
<l>amma vāḻi tōḻi ciṟiyilai</l>
<l>nelli nīṭiya kalkāy kaṭattiṭaip</l>
<l>pētai neñcam piṉcelac ceṉṟōr</l>
<l>kalliṉum valiyar maṉṟa</l>
<l>pallita ḻuṇka ṇaḻappirin tōrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Alas! May you live long, my friend! </l>
<l>He who has gone, and made my silly heart go after [him] </l>
<l>through the hot wilderness, where on the rocks  </l>
<l>Nelli trees with small leaves rise high, </l>
<l>he who has left, and made my many-petalled collyrium eyes cry, </l>
<l>is indeed harder than stone. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
